oracle.adf.controller.metadata.model
Interface View

All Superinterfaces:
Activity, AdfcNode, IdHolder, NodeHolder, TrainStopContainer, UIInfo
public interface View
extends Activity, TrainStopContainer

Represents metadata for a view activity. For example, 

  <view>
    <page>/folderA/folderB/aReallyCoolPage.jspx</page>
     <bookmark/>
  </view>
